thread/1674226/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ghYVsH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ghYVsH.png&h=5a840d64&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"其實衝閘好危險，呢排見到黨鐵有好多附例隊睇住閘口，比人捉住可能受到暴力虐待，而且月台係死路，走唔切一定比人捉住，社運越多人越安全，不如一齊約去貼文宣好過，黨鐵主要收入係地產，跳閘減唔到幾多票務收入，留有用之驅做宣或經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n行動<br />\n、換美金走資開離岸戶口買美股<br />\n、只用現金，減少消費，罷買中資<br />\n、本地用美金不用港幣<br />\n、MPF轉環球股票/美國股票<br />\n<br />\n香港良心經濟圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1M_y7COGzbXIdJWOr5EUSG6fULi8eGGtu&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.342499370860658%2C114.10534086977282&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1M_y7COGzbXIdJWOr5EUSG6fULi8eGGtu%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.342499370860658%252C114.10534086977282%26z%3D11&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=c5bec53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1M_y7COGzbXIdJWOr5EUSG6fULi8eGGtu&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.342499370860658%2C114.10534086977282&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n罷買品牌 (可用搜索功能)<br />\n、書: 三聯/中華/商務<br />\n、食: 吉野家/美心/富臨/7-11/惠康/萬寧/M記/PIZZA HUT/KFC/元氣/STARBUCKS/優品360/華潤<br />\n、銀行: 中國銀行/永隆/東亞銀行/南洋商業/建設銀行/交通銀行/招商/中信/光大/浦東/興業/創興/集友/工商/上海銀行/華夏/廣發/平安<br />\n、錢: 八達通/淘寶/支付寶/人民幣/人民幣國債<br />\n、電子:中移動/中電信/中聯通/華為/小米/VIVO/聯想/微信<br />\n、行:中航/中旅社<br />\n<br />\n一人N個 推!!!"},{"pid":"530b779bd0c8286c3108bd8ddee1d77979f54fcc","tid":1674752,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3rZEXN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3rZEXN.gif&h=b0a1f406&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"821c2746a4a58bf8df2e7d7c2c1d79bd51de54a5","tid":1674752,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e846338e726b55df05b5a398a9315dd1f69f4d43","tid":1674752,"uid":48679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"人人借盡9成按買樓<br />\n然後一齊唔還, 由佢收樓,爆硬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"傻豬 銀主盤拍賣大把人接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92ee41e51524db9d667a1f4c422a0ffa0903606","tid":1674752,"uid":97389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cc75b2f555a543d02d943c85f61503358f9bd3c9","tid":1674752,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"其實我地係唔係無辦法癱瘓到香港融資能力?<br />\n好似無計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"要癱瘓融資能力要講經濟最基本的一樣嘢: <span style=\"color: red;\">信心</span>.<br />\n只要投資者有信心危機, 認為危險/騙局/回唔到本/D錢走唔到, 求其中一樣. 就唔會肯落注一個市場.<br />\n而信心危機呢樣嘢, 自港共開始用緊急法呢隻無限手套開始就急劇惡化. 呢個時間, 只要美帝再開打金融戰, 對港共施壓. 香港吸外資能力就會再幾何級數下降.<br />\n香港人可以做的, 就係<span style=\"color: red;\">繼續和平示威/不合作/超合作運動爭取5大訴求缺一不可</span>, 對港共持續施壓. 管治危機, 政權的威信危機, 法院的法治危機會直接演變成信心危機. 大家睇清楚D, 依D影響而家已經慢慢浮面."},{"pid":"a07fc20efb429637af678ffaf7633b2fc855d076","tid":1674752,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"014736a9d45eb64288f1c8662891703d2b08d6dc","tid":1674752,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:46:30.000Z","msg":"1萬人裝修港交所 即贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"6月頭到依家仲有傻閪話搞港膠所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb30be5cd267b4297f3db6ef43e63d8b7a7fbd1d","tid":1674752,"uid":284592,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"冇必要癱瘓，針對黑色国企就OK。"},{"pid":"db346cf4d1b2468f8a8f0b17b97993ccc6e00d83","tid":1674752,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"821c2746a4a58bf8df2e7d7c2c1d79bd51de54a5","tid":1674752,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e846338e726b55df05b5a398a9315dd1f69f4d43","tid":1674752,"uid":48679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"人人借盡9成按買樓<br />\n然後一齊唔還, 由佢收樓,爆硬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T1